```plantuml
@startuml domingo1021_Bunny-code

actor User
participant "Nginx (Reverse Proxy)" as Nginx
participant "Express API" as API
participant "Socket.IO" as Socket
participant "MySQL Database" as MySQL
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis
participant "Docker Sandbox" as Sandbox
participant "S3 Storage" as S3

User -> Nginx : HTTPS Request (API/WebSocket)
Nginx -> API : Proxy API Request
API -> MySQL : Query Data
MySQL --> API : Return Data
API -> Redis : Check Cache
Redis --> API : Return Cached Data (or null)
API -> Sandbox : Execute Code (Docker)
Sandbox --> API : Execution Results
API -> S3 : Store/Retrieve Files
S3 --> API : File Operations Result
API --> Nginx : API Response
Nginx --> User : HTTPS Response

User -> Nginx : WebSocket Connection
Nginx -> Socket : Upgrade Connection
Socket -> Redis : Validate Session
Redis --> Socket : Session Data
Socket --> Nginx : WebSocket Established
Nginx --> User : WebSocket Connected

User -> Socket : Real-time Event (e.g., code edit)
Socket -> Redis : Update Shared State
Redis --> Socket : State Updated
Socket -> API : Persist Changes (optional)
API -> MySQL : Update Database
MySQL --> API : Update Confirmation
Socket --> User : Broadcast Update

@enduml
```